text:
Calling all history and civics teachers!

We are partnering with the National Constitution Center (@ConstitutionCtr) to invite you to our exclusive webinar on June 21 at 10:30 AM PST.

Join us to:

✨ Empower your students with a profound understanding of the Constitution
✨ Develop a personalized plan to bring the Constitution 101 student course to your classroom
✨ Explore NCC's teacher resources, including live classes, lesson plans, and more

We’ll walk you through everything step-by-step!

PLUS - discover how the Constitution 101 course can transform your teaching:

➡️ Supercharge Learning: Leverage renowned scholars, primary sources, and Khan Academy's AI to deepen your students' understanding of the Constitution.
➡️ Personalized Strategies: Discover methods for personalized learning and bridging the civics education gap.
➡️ Seamless Integration: Get tips for seamlessly incorporating this nonpartisan resource into your existing curriculum.

Spots are limited! Register now: https://t.co/5xz9v1teqr
